{"tid":847010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"庫克暗批Facebook、Google 靠賣用戶資料賺錢","createTime":"2018-10-04T00:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T09:38:52.000Z","uid":28765,"like":14,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"025423a5c162ec4e4a0578fc73d80e8bada90e1e","tid":847010,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:26:37.000Z","msg":"蘋果執行長庫克批評，某些科技公司「更多客戶資訊能導出更好產品」的說法，是滿口胡言。<br />\n<br />\n庫克2日在Vice News Tonight播出的訪談中，雖沒明說那些科技公司是誰，但很明顯指的是靠著把用戶資訊分享給第三者、因而得到大量廣告利益的臉書（Facebook）和谷歌（Google）。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，「有些公司的說法，試圖讓你相信：『我們必須取得用戶你的所有資訊，來讓我們的服務更加完善』」，「但可千萬不要相信他們！」對你這麼說的人，根本是在瞎扯。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果向來對用戶的隱私保護特別留意，每次推出新產品都會增加外界取得使用者資料的難度。公司最新的政策規定所有的應用程式（App）業者必須說明，會如何運用用戶的個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n庫克說自己不是喜歡法令規章的人，但是他樂意配合立法部門，「一定程度的立法規範，有其重要性」，以確保科技公司的產品服務對社會帶來益處。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果今年稍早將掌管中國iCloud用戶的資料中心移到中國境內，引起是否會讓中國當局更容易取得用戶資料的批評。庫克重申，蘋果在全球各地的保密政策完全一致，即使是在中國大陸，蘋果對客戶的資料也不會妥協，必定善加保護。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6811/3401945?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6811%2F3401945%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catelistnews_ch2&d=H3DcRIHP3HVBLs8OlYA0uhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=e69e53f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6811/3401945?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"b0f5ed69bba53baab7af1c844140f0498b5764f6","tid":847010,"uid":44171,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:35:52.000Z","msg":"記得有單新聞係美國既支那佬買左iphone, 但個icloud係貴州雲, sync左d問題data上去連iphone都lock埋, 連蘋果自己都解唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a0ef81dbb7c5c2dfb857e30056d279defc7648","tid":847010,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:36:31.000Z","msg":"成個icloud畀支那管就唔係？一句會保護就過骨"},{"pid":"4f0fd00db4e4b9c8f69aa62db404155045ced531","tid":847010,"uid":109462,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:41:54.000Z","msg":"一時唔偷雞做保長，五十步笑百步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6689b17a6635b52d49de715c422c2977fcc0c90","tid":847010,"uid":56698,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:45:46.000Z","msg":"講到自己冇份咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effd38b57fa76ec15bc934325ab64bdc83f2664c","tid":847010,"uid":44358,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T00:58:44.000Z","msg":"原來賣個 cloud 換生意就好高尚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4924096dcb54c3c3b24a23e83bbb212d28355d2","tid":847010,"uid":113000,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T02:03:57.000Z","msg":"將用戶出賣俾中共冇問題?"},{"pid":"fc10844679bffed2f9f678bb43e4341e7965d521","tid":847010,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T02:46:47.000Z","msg":"係咪淨中國 icloud 使用者先會去雲上貴州已經成疑"},{"pid":"6edf09eefc57503c416250fb1eae8e9c4a0f2607","tid":847010,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc10844679bffed2f9f678bb43e4341e7965d521","tid":847010,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T02:46:47.000Z","msg":"係咪淨中國 icloud 使用者先會去雲上貴州已經成疑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T02:49:55.000Z","msg":"一句「自古以來」就可以將美國列入固有領土 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6002004b1a960f2709b725d0ecc48b6b2afba1c9","tid":847010,"uid":5159,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6edf09eefc57503c416250fb1eae8e9c4a0f2607","tid":847010,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc10844679bffed2f9f678bb43e4341e7965d521","tid":847010,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T02:46:47.000Z","msg":"係咪淨中國 icloud 使用者先會去雲上貴州已經成疑"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T02:49:55.000Z","msg":"一句「自古以來」就可以將美國列入固有領土 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T02:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img